        <h1 style="font-size: var(--fs-4xl);">Lassen Volcanic: Emerald Lake, Lake Helen, and the hydrothermal basins.</h1>
        <p class="lede">
          Lassen is a study in volcanism you can actually walk through. Four
          different volcano types share the skyline. Boiling mud pots bubble
          a hundred yards off the main highway. And in spring, Emerald Lake
          doesn't look real.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="container">
        <figure class="article-hero">
